{"tid":1496332,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[823核彈]  馬尼拉人質事件 9週年","createTime":"2019-08-22T13:05:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-23T07:59:06.000Z","uid":60136,"like":46,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"1b7370aa79d70c17321255bee1f7d7287da93414","tid":1496332,"uid":60136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T13:05:44.000Z","msg":"馬尼拉人質事件，菲律賓政府稱為黎剎公園人質事件（英語：Rizal Park Hostage-taking Incident），香港特區政府稱為馬尼拉人質事件（英語：Manila Hostage Crisis）或菲律賓人質事件，是一場發生於2010年8月23日的劫持事件。菲港兩地政府在達成解決方案的聯合公報，英文統稱為基尼諾大看台事件（英語：Quirino Grandstand Incident）。中華人民共和國政府稱為8&middot;23香港人質事件。<br />\n<br />\n2010年8月23日菲律賓馬尼拉時間上午約9時半，被革除的菲律賓國家警察前高級督察羅蘭多&middot;門多薩強行登上一輛屬於香港康泰旅行社旅行團的旅遊巴士，挾持車上包括遊客、司機、導遊、領隊和攝影師，共25名人質，要求菲律賓政府恢復他的職務。綁匪先後釋放了9名人質，另外1名菲律賓籍司機人質成功逃脫。事件持續近10小時後，匪徒與特種武器和戰術部隊爆發槍戰，救援行動多次暫停，後者進攻逾1小時後，最終由狙擊手擊斃綁匪。事件持續12小時後，以15名人質中7名受傷、8名死亡，及匪徒死亡告終。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E9%A6%AC%E5%B0%BC%E6%8B%89%E4%BA%BA%E8%B3%AA%E4%BA%8B%E4%BB%B6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E9%25A6%25AC%25E5%25B0%25BC%25E6%258B%2589%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%25B3%25AA%25E4%25BA%258B%25E4%25BB%25B6&d=eywEaFxHh3WcM61vPhP2LR5ZC4%2B%2BlHDPeg0yH0hWprM%3D&h=12e1bb29\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E9%A6%AC%E5%B0%BC%E6%8B%89%E4%BA%BA%E8%B3%AA%E4%BA%8B%E4%BB%B6</a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">點解菲律賓人射香港人就港殤，香港警察就放題式任射!!!</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"538ee206f28c6de37f82d42195a236c03f2b6abf","tid":1496332,"uid":60136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T13:09:12.000Z","msg":"推啊"},{"pid":"38811dcdf34443dc2773bd03cf52b8ae383f9de7","tid":1496332,"uid":60136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T13:10:30.000Z","msg":"推啊"},{"pid":"f46274ab6eb544a48016c0f8215ac8426ef7dbab","tid":1496332,"uid":187489,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T13:10:39.000Z","msg":"歷歷在目"},{"pid":"d1f073074bc61777b0abafbbda427b55a085079c","tid":1496332,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T13:11:51.000Z","msg":"香港警犬同馬尼拉警一樣咁垃圾"},{"pid":"927b455a0d019dc63392a44d41abcfc80c131005","tid":1496332,"uid":60136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T13:11:52.000Z","msg":"推啊 連登仔!!!"},{"pid":"8217360f75a376a19fbe2326d02f56282a887f0f","tid":1496332,"uid":60136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T13:13:30.000Z","msg":"幫手推POST啊"},{"pid":"24b88d1fd8e2a458bf0b673fe2159dd6fd17ab63","tid":1496332,"uid":286441,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T13:13:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">咪一樣！！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OuTzQFK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOuTzQFK.jpg&h=49111a0c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cbf5d8abbacb361d229d6f550351b08201a6907a","tid":1496332,"uid":60136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T13:15:30.000Z","msg":"推推推推"},{"pid":"e56299e0033c7088cabed1fad3f4957fd8023c9a","tid":1496332,"uid":186997,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T13:15:39.000Z","msg":"嗰時以為賓賓國嗰啲差佬已經夠垃圾，估唔到一山還有一山低嘅香港警察<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e